00:00:11.976 --> 00:00:14.029
ken dos nisht fargesn, keyn mol.

00:00:15.182 --> 00:00:17.218
azoy vi ⟨ikh ze, s'hot⟩ UNK ⟨alts⟩.

00:00:20.312 --> 00:00:26.246
froy RAKHEL Gutman, mir geyen foroys mit undzer intervyu, bay CASSETTE numer tsvey.

00:00:26.269 --> 00:00:28.085
bite, dertseyln zi vayter.

00:00:30.117 --> 00:00:32.051
m- m'hot zikh nokh avekgezetst,

00:00:32.091 --> 00:00:37.074
derfar vos m'hot geklert, ⟨az er, er⟩ hot gezogt er geyt in shtub arayn onklingen tsu der, keyn Holevne,

00:00:37.074 --> 00:00:38.430
in der politsey.

00:00:38.638 --> 00:00:40.598
kumt aroys zayn eydem,

00:00:40.598 --> 00:00:42.024
der tsveyter bandit,

00:00:42.182 --> 00:00:47.339
un zogt, "⟨TY ZNAYESH, TUT BYL SHMUL'KO⟩," der bruder mayner, mit Meyer London.

00:00:47.818 --> 00:00:52.340
"nu," kler ikh, "do lign zey shoyn zikher." vayl Meyer London iz geven a groyser gevir.

00:00:52.340 --> 00:00:54.025
er hot gehat a shnit-gesheft.

00:00:55.108 --> 00:00:56.317
un

00:00:56.526 --> 00:01:02.209
s'iz nishto keyn breyre. un er makht khoyzek fun undz, un er geyt arayn in shtub arayn. s'iz fraytik-tsu-nakhts.

00:01:02.209 --> 00:01:03.776
oyf der gas iz sheyn.

00:01:03.867 --> 00:01:07.677
likhtik. di levone shaynt, az ir kent shraybn, azoy vi ⟨oyf a tselokhes⟩.

00:01:07.677 --> 00:01:10.833
ir kent leyenen bay der levone. ⟨kler⟩, "reboyne-shel-oylem,

00:01:10.833 --> 00:01:13.583
makh epes, s'zol vern fintster, s'zol geyn regenen."

00:01:13.583 --> 00:01:18.043
azoy zenen ts- un di minut gut vern, ⟨az mayn tokhter zol⟩,

00:01:18.043 --> 00:01:19.638
vi in der minut

00:01:19.813 --> 00:01:21.410
iz gevorn a nepl,

00:01:21.653 --> 00:01:23.689
un s'hot ongehoybn azoy proshen a regn,

00:01:23.689 --> 00:01:25.818
un m'hot zikh nokh avekgezetst hinter der vant.

00:01:25.818 --> 00:01:27.750
ven es hot ongehoybn gut regenen,

00:01:27.750 --> 00:01:33.527
hot er gekhapt dos meydele un ikh dos yingele, un m'iz arayngelofn, koydem zenen mir arayngelofn in a veldl,

00:01:34.444 --> 00:01:37.613
azoy ⟨vartn mir⟩ in, in di, in di, in di blotes,

00:01:37.613 --> 00:01:39.298
in d- in di vaser.

00:01:40.333 --> 00:01:47.296
a fus arayn, a fus aroys fun di blotes, zog ikh, z⟨UNK⟩ vi me fleg zen in kino. me fleg geyn in kino un flegn mir zen aza zakh.

00:01:47.623 --> 00:01:53.034
un m'hot a g- halbe nakht azoy umgeblondzhet in dem veldl. dernokh, ⟨heyb⟩ ikh on tsu mayn bruder,

00:01:53.108 --> 00:01:54.640
"ver zhe veystu dort?"

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:56.463
zogt er, er veyst eyn goy,

00:01:56.463 --> 00:01:58.232
eyn, shtub,

00:01:58.255 --> 00:02:01.117
vos ⟨ir⟩ ken er, un dem foter ken er,

00:02:01.225 --> 00:02:04.916
vos er voynt, lebn dem, er ⟨hot gev-⟩ koyft a goy a sod,

00:02:04.916 --> 00:02:06.259
iz voynen zey derlebn.

00:02:06.259 --> 00:02:11.344
nor dem, sheygets vos ⟨er hot⟩ UNK, di goye hot khasene gehat, ken er nisht. er iz geven a oremer sheygets.

00:02:11.518 --> 00:02:15.109
"kum, lomir pruvn arayngeyn ibernekhtikn ⟨di⟩ nakht, s'iz fraytik-tsu-nakhts."

00:02:15.109 --> 00:02:18.616
aheymgekumen, nisht loyfn vayl di, di politsey iz oyf yedn trit un shrit.

00:02:19.585 --> 00:02:22.796
⟨nor⟩ der bruder zet nisht. er molt mir oys vu s'iz.

00:02:22.796 --> 00:02:27.141
un ikh fir im tsu tsu eyn klinye, zogt er, "do iz dos nisht," vedlik ikh mol im oys.

00:02:27.141 --> 00:02:29.411
tsu der tsveyter klinye, "do iz dos nisht."

00:02:29.411 --> 00:02:33.175
tsu der driter klinye, me kumt tsu, me geyt aroyf oyfn, dem ⟨PIDVOROK⟩,

00:02:33.810 --> 00:02:39.831
ikh efn oyf di, di tir. zogt er, "do darf zayn otave, hey aza." m'iz geven nas in gantsn.

00:02:39.831 --> 00:02:43.491
⟨zogt mir⟩, "efn nokh ⟨eyn⟩ tir fun di, fun der klinye." iz shtroy.

00:02:43.513 --> 00:02:47.518
zogt er, "efn nokh a tir." me g⟨eyt arayn in⟩ der tsveyter tir: otave, hey,

00:02:47.518 --> 00:02:50.477
un me krikht arayn in der otave, nas,

00:02:50.567 --> 00:02:52.080
kalt un nas,

00:02:52.255 --> 00:02:54.038
un er hot gefunen a shtik broyt.

00:02:55.073 --> 00:02:59.447
zog ikh, "do efsher ⟨veln mir⟩ shoyn zitsn. a shtik broyt gefunen in der fintster, bay nakht!

00:02:59.447 --> 00:03:01.238
azoy vi emetser volt ongegreyt."

00:03:01.238 --> 00:03:04.477
un ikh tsebrekh bald un gib di kinder, ir a shtikl un im a shtikl,

00:03:04.477 --> 00:03:07.217
nokh dray tog vos zey hobn shoyn nisht gegesn, nokh fir tog.

00:03:07.594 --> 00:03:12.910
zog ikh, "efsher vet got helfn, do vet men zitsn." ⟨ay,⟩ di kinder heybn nokh on, d⟨UNK⟩

00:03:12.910 --> 00:03:17.004
UNK, UNK, me zol vern trukn koydem di fis,

00:03:17.162 --> 00:03:20.362
se vert azoy vi far tog, azoy bay di goyim.

00:03:20.419 --> 00:03:24.862
un er hot, ⟨er hot⟩, gegat a plimenik a MOSKVICH, KHARTON hot er geheysn,

00:03:24.862 --> 00:03:27.028
iz er gegan gibn di beheymes esn.

00:03:27.591 --> 00:03:31.509
er iz tsugekumen, hot er gezen nit farmakht di klinye, un di klinye iz ofn.

00:03:31.509 --> 00:03:32.979
iz er shoyn nisht arayngegan,

00:03:32.979 --> 00:03:35.280
nor er iz gegan aroysrufn dem balebos.

00:03:35.320 --> 00:03:37.913
er, vi er geyt oyfn veg, zogt er, "KHARTON!"

00:03:38.205 --> 00:03:42.637
der, er hot geredt rusish, der KHARTON. "MOZHET TY NE POMNISH'? MOZHET TY NE ZAKRYL?"

00:03:42.694 --> 00:03:46.451
zogt er, "NET, DYADYA! YA KHOROSHO POMNYU, YA ZAKRYL!"

00:03:47.470 --> 00:03:54.011
un er zingt zikh tsu, der balebos, "VYKHODILA NA BEREG KATYUSHA." er geyt azoy freylekh un zingt zikh tsu.

00:03:54.405 --> 00:03:57.834
un er geyt arayn in klinye. zogt er, "ISHCHI KU⟨UNK⟩LO"

00:03:58.371 --> 00:04:00.069
er zol zukhn, v-

00:04:00.683 --> 00:04:04.524
geyt shoyn tsu mayn bruder. zogt, "ANISKI?" zogt er, "ikh bin do do."

00:04:05.357 --> 00:04:07.716
er dertseylt nisht fun mir mit di kinder.

00:04:07.716 --> 00:04:08.712
zogt er, "nu,

00:04:08.712 --> 00:04:11.082
"⟨PRINOCHYVAL, TO IDIT' SOBI⟩"

00:04:11.230 --> 00:04:13.519
zogt er, "vi zhe ken ikh atsind aroysgeyn?"

00:04:13.525 --> 00:04:15.066
s'iz shabes in der fri.

00:04:15.066 --> 00:04:18.666
di, ale ukraynishe politsyantn flegn oyf shabes aheymgeyn.

00:04:19.701 --> 00:04:23.239
zogt er, "vi zhe ken ikh atsind aheymgeyn?" "nu," zogt er, "zitst shoyn ibern tog."

00:04:23.312 --> 00:04:24.996
m'hot gehert aza, vi,

00:04:24.996 --> 00:04:27.434
er, er, ⟨m'hot dem,⟩ hot men keyn trunk nisht gevolt gebn.

00:04:27.434 --> 00:04:31.611
un geyt arayn in shtub arayn un brengt arayn a tepl kartoflyes mit a fleshl vaser,

00:04:31.611 --> 00:04:32.958
mit a shtikl broyt.

00:04:33.319 --> 00:04:36.898
dos iz geven dos, nisht tsum bashraybn, nisht tsum dertseyln,

00:04:36.898 --> 00:04:38.882
vos far a luksus dos iz geven damlst.

00:04:40.187 --> 00:04:43.500
un ikh heyb shoyn on dem bruder zogn, "red mit im, red mit im!"

00:04:43.500 --> 00:04:45.477
⟨un⟩ se kumt fraytik-tsu-nakhts...

00:04:46.195 --> 00:04:49.170
dos iz shoyn geven shabes bay nakht... kumt er arayn in klinye

00:04:49.170 --> 00:04:51.591
un brengt arayn nokh a tepl kartoflyes,

00:04:51.591 --> 00:04:55.723
un er zetst zikh avek mit im, mitn bruder redn. zogt er, "du veyst?

00:04:55.729 --> 00:04:58.961
dayn bruder Moyshe," der vos iz geven in Amerike,

00:04:58.961 --> 00:05:01.273
"hot mir a mol a groyse toyve getun.

00:05:01.382 --> 00:05:05.936
ven ikh tu aykh op a toyve, veys ikh az er, az er volt mir vayter opgedint."

00:05:05.936 --> 00:05:09.738
m'hert aza vort? ikh her zikh nor tsu oyfn ⟨hey⟩, ⟨vi azoy er redt⟩.

00:05:10.157 --> 00:05:13.210
zog ikh, "Yidl"... er, er, der bruder iz shoyn geven azoy ⟨fartamlt⟩...

00:05:13.210 --> 00:05:16.930
zog ikh, "Yidl, di, m⟨UNK⟩ shoyn fun danen. do muz men shoyn zen epes tsu tun."

00:05:16.930 --> 00:05:20.411
⟨zog⟩, "⟨gey⟩ red im ayn goldene glikn." er veyst az er iz geven a groyser soykher,

00:05:20.620 --> 00:05:25.930
un er veyst az er hot tsugeholfn di vayb zayne tsu koyfn dort dem, a sod hot zi ge⟨ga⟩t gekoyft.

00:05:26.138 --> 00:05:29.692
un er heybt im on tsuzogn goldene glikn. un er zogt, "nu,

00:05:30.289 --> 00:05:32.240
zayts do tsvey-dray khadoshim."

00:05:32.533 --> 00:05:36.866
ir veyst vos s'iz damlst geven eyn, zayn "tsvey-dray"? haynt darf ikh shoyn nisht dertseyln,

00:05:36.866 --> 00:05:38.909
vos s'hot geheysn zayn "tsvey-dray khadoshim."

00:05:38.909 --> 00:05:41.425
azoy vi ale toytn ⟨zene⟩n oyfgeshtanen fun der erd.

00:05:42.388 --> 00:05:45.971
dos iz geven shabes, un zuntik fort er mit der vayb keyn Libevne,

00:05:45.971 --> 00:05:49.756
un di vayb zet az me f- firt aroys lebn undzer shtub tsvey-dray hundert yidn,

00:05:49.780 --> 00:05:52.575
un zi kumt tsu geyn, zi vil nisht far keyn shum gelt.

00:05:52.767 --> 00:05:55.225
far keyn shum gelt! me zol shoyn avekgeyn.

00:05:55.872 --> 00:05:59.872
un er hot gefirt a groysn kamf. der goy hot gefirt mit ir a groysn kamf.

00:05:59.872 --> 00:06:03.222
un m'iz geblibn vayter zitsn. der KHARTON kumt arayn, zogt er,

00:06:03.330 --> 00:06:06.378
"YA," zogt er, "PODSLUSHALSYA NOCH'YU," zogt er,

00:06:06.604 --> 00:06:10.850
"KAK ⟨I- T- I-⟩ TYOTYA," zogt er, "GOVORIL, GOVORILA S DYADYU."

00:06:11.312 --> 00:06:13.196
"⟨I VY ESHCHYO⟩ BUDITE ZDES'."

00:06:13.354 --> 00:06:16.464
un brengt arayn shtilerheyt, ganvet aroys a por ⟨PIROZHKI⟩s,

00:06:16.464 --> 00:06:18.083
un brengt undz arayn.

00:06:19.918 --> 00:06:28.683
ANISKI kumt arayn un m'heybt im shoyn on, aynredn, un, derlebn iz geven vos mayn bruder, der Meyer, hot gegat dort avekgeshtelt

00:06:28.683 --> 00:06:32.631
f-, peltsn, vayl far di, sovyetn, hobn ⟨zey dokh⟩ alts tsugenumen,

00:06:32.631 --> 00:06:34.729
un er hot gegat dort zeyer a sakh tvue,

00:06:34.988 --> 00:06:36.076
vol.

00:06:36.076 --> 00:06:42.184
zogt er, "kh'vel dir gebn, brengen a por zeklekh vol." vayl di goye fleg arbetn fun vol, fleg zi shpinen epes dort.

00:06:43.307 --> 00:06:45.039
un der bruder geyt avek

00:06:45.433 --> 00:06:52.092
un b- vil brengen di, dem pelts mit di vol. er tut zikh on dem pelts un brengt di tsvey zeker vol, un vert farblondzhet.

00:06:52.605 --> 00:06:54.618
zet nisht vi tsuriktsugeyn.

00:06:53.702 --> 00:06:54.675
der Yidl?

00:06:54.618 --> 00:06:57.643
yo, der Yidl. s'iz geven tsutsugeyn, zog ikh, fun danet,

00:06:57.643 --> 00:06:59.062
 a glaykher veg,

00:06:59.338 --> 00:07:01.120
fuftsik meter, nisht mer.

00:07:01.347 --> 00:07:02.944
vey! vos tut men?

00:07:03.186 --> 00:07:05.829
⟨er⟩... ikh blayb mit tsvey kinder un,

00:07:06.358 --> 00:07:08.680
in der fri, s'iz shoyn likhtik,

00:07:09.058 --> 00:07:13.025
 di shiksl shrayt, tsu, tsu KHARTON, tsu der muter,

00:07:13.345 --> 00:07:15.988
"⟨MAMA, KAKOY-TO DED ZAYSHOL V KLUNI⟩."

00:07:16.568 --> 00:07:18.176
un zi hot shoyn gevust

00:07:18.176 --> 00:07:19.917
vos do ⟨iz geshen⟩.

00:07:19.917 --> 00:07:22.515
zogt zi, "⟨OY, KAKOY-TO DURNOY DED ZAYSHOL⟩."

00:07:22.515 --> 00:07:28.225
un der KHARTON kumt arayn. zogt er, di goye vil nisht atsind. "TYOTYA NE KHOCHET, NI ZA CHTO, zogt zi,

00:07:28.225 --> 00:07:29.758
tomer hot men dikh gezen."

00:07:30.355 --> 00:07:36.267
un m'hot farloyrn aza plats! shtelt zikh for. m'hot zikh oyfgegesn. m'hot zikh oyfgegesn eyner dem andern.

00:07:36.267 --> 00:07:40.721
un mir betn nor got, az me zol nisht dermanen. ANISKI kumt arayn un,

00:07:40.721 --> 00:07:42.680
"vos hostu getun aza zakh?"

00:07:43.264 --> 00:07:45.923
"nu," zogt er, "m'vet nisht dermanen der nomen,

00:07:45.923 --> 00:07:47.223
vet ir zitsn do."

00:07:47.668 --> 00:07:48.918
got helft!

00:07:48.918 --> 00:07:53.029
tsu im kumt men ale tog, ale zuntik bay nakht un me leyent di BIBLIYA.

00:07:53.220 --> 00:07:55.166
me leyent oys in der BIBLIYA

00:07:55.166 --> 00:07:57.064
az, ale taybelekh

00:07:57.064 --> 00:07:59.761
veln gefroyrn vern in dray un fertsikstn yor.

00:08:00.561 --> 00:08:05.629
nor di taybelekh vos di, di mentshn veln araynnemen in di shtiber arayn, di taybelekh veln blaybn.

00:08:05.629 --> 00:08:10.477
"di taybelekh," zogt er, zi- zitsn di, vos zey lernen di BIBLIYA, "zenen di yidn.

00:08:10.804 --> 00:08:13.211
ver s'vet araynnemen a yid, der vet blaybn."

00:08:14.787 --> 00:08:16.543
shoyn avade gut!

00:08:16.710 --> 00:08:21.052
un m'iz gezitsn, un m'iz azoy dervayl geblibn zitsn in meshekh fun der tsayt,

00:08:21.052 --> 00:08:23.049
iz geven kalts un varems.

00:08:23.072 --> 00:08:27.892
zi hot nisht gevolt, me zol zayn, vos zey hobn azoy geforn in shtot arayn un zi iz tsurikgekumen,"nu, me zol avekgeyn."

00:08:28.489 --> 00:08:31.040
m'iz gezitsn, on a K⟨UNK⟩.

00:08:31.408 --> 00:08:36.262
opgezitsn, vinter iz men opgezitsn in eyn hemd, di gantse tsayt gezitsn in eyn hemd.

00:08:36.505 --> 00:08:40.777
nokh fuftsn khadoshim hot zikh dos hemd tserisn. m'iz gegan in shlengelekh oyf zikh.

00:08:40.777 --> 00:08:44.477
di kinder farvoglt gevorn mi- mit di, mit di layz,

00:08:44.477 --> 00:08:49.763
mit di, mit di layz, mit di shtshures. s'iz geven a fintster, a fintsterer ort oyf di vishkes,

00:08:50.443 --> 00:08:53.559
vos er hot aroyfgeleygt a bisl shtroy un dort zenen mir gelegn.

00:08:55.843 --> 00:08:59.991
⟨ nishto⟩, ⟨d- he⟩, dos yingele heybt on veynen, "oder sam mir, oder heng mir."

00:08:59.991 --> 00:09:02.722
"oder sam mir oder heng mir! ikh ken nisht laydn keyn hunger!"

00:09:03.066 --> 00:09:05.343
