00:09:05.614 --> 00:09:08.595
"na!" kh'nem a pasik, ikh gib ⟨es⟩, zog ikh, "na, heng zikh oyf!"

00:09:08.787 --> 00:09:11.298
vos men ken tun? s'iz nisht geven vos tsu tun.

00:09:11.298 --> 00:09:14.898
⟨ah, un zi,⟩ dos meydele hot geterpet un er hot gehaltn in eyn veynen.

00:09:14.898 --> 00:09:16.138
veynen un shrayen.

00:09:16.228 --> 00:09:17.451
un, un...

00:09:18.608 --> 00:09:23.169
helft nokh got. der, zey, m'iz gezitsn in der shtal fun di beheymes,

00:09:23.169 --> 00:09:25.446
un di beheymes hobn gegat kelbelekh,

00:09:25.446 --> 00:09:28.276
un der goy hot gegat a shvoger a politsyant.

00:09:28.276 --> 00:09:32.371
un kumt zuntik tsu geyn un geyt arayn in shtal arayn kukn, oyf di, oyf di kelbelekh.

00:09:32.371 --> 00:09:36.000
un dos yingele halt azoy arop dem kop un kukt oykh oyf di kelbelekh.

00:09:36.225 --> 00:09:41.484
di vishkes ⟨iz⟩ UNK geven breyte, nisht keyn ⟨UNK⟩ne, m- gan-, dos gantse ponem zet men aroys.

00:09:42.520 --> 00:09:44.061
er ken zikh shoyn nisht rirn.

00:09:44.061 --> 00:09:47.678
⟨gey rays ikh op MAMASH⟩ dos ponem, me ken im nisht tsuriktsien, me ken gornisht tun.

00:09:48.561 --> 00:09:53.274
