00:09:53.274 --> 00:09:54.528
un er iz aroysgegan.

00:09:55.007 --> 00:09:57.079
un undz ze'mir geblibn vayter zitsn.

00:09:57.079 --> 00:09:59.874
m'iz geblibn vayter zitsn. kumt in,

00:09:59.874 --> 00:10:04.232
in YANVAR kumen tsu geyn, di daytshn. m'hot farkhapt ir tokhter oyf arbet.

00:10:04.440 --> 00:10:12.155
di goye hot gegat nokh a tokhter fun ⟨frierer⟩; ven zi hot im khasene, ven zi hot khasene gehat mit im, hot zi gegat a, a shiksl fun frier.

00:10:12.155 --> 00:10:16.343
un me farkhapt di, di UNK zi veynt, zi shrayt. zi vil nisht,

00:10:16.343 --> 00:10:18.289
zi vil nisht hern afile me zol zayn.

00:10:18.970 --> 00:10:24.525
"⟨ver⟩," zogt zi, "keyn eyn yid iz shoyn nishto. vos iz," zogt zi, "do tsu zitsn? ale yidn zenen shoyn oysgeharget."

00:10:25.618 --> 00:10:27.124
azoy zenen mir opgezitsn

00:10:27.124 --> 00:10:30.287
dem vinter, un dem zumer, un nokh a vinter.

00:10:31.677 --> 00:10:35.923
un me, u- in hunger, ⟨MAMASH⟩ in hunger. dem tsveytn vinter

00:10:36.064 --> 00:10:38.370
ven, ven in dray un fertsikstn yor,

00:10:38.410 --> 00:10:40.971
ven, s'iz gezitsn bay im di mishpokhe,

00:10:40.971 --> 00:10:43.364
un me dertseylt vi m'hot gezen mayn bruder,

00:10:43.810 --> 00:10:46.588
mayne tsvey brider zitsn ⟨dort un⟩ dortn,

00:10:46.628 --> 00:10:48.562
bay im in a prizbe.

00:10:49.210 --> 00:10:53.847
nem ikh un shrayb on a brivl un der goy geyt avek mit dem brivl tsu di brider.

00:10:53.847 --> 00:10:56.358
un di tsvey brider, der bruder Meyer,

00:10:56.466 --> 00:10:58.519
er iz geven zeyer, aza

00:10:58.609 --> 00:10:59.956
⟨shtele oyf⟩ zikh.

00:10:59.956 --> 00:11:02.045
er hot zikh getrofn mit di partizaner,

00:11:04.482 --> 00:11:11.059
un er zogt, azoy vet men nisht brengen, oyb s'vet nisht, zayn, oyb s'vet zikh fartsien di milkhome,

00:11:11.059 --> 00:11:12.828
brengt er Shmuel tsu undz,

00:11:14.067 --> 00:11:16.052
un er vet geyn in di partizaner.

00:11:18.454 --> 00:11:21.603
dos iz geven, dos iz geven montik,

00:11:21.846 --> 00:11:28.320
zuntik un montik zenen zey avekgegan tsu dem goy un donershtik ⟨iz⟩, zenen ku- tsugekumen di daytshn brenen dem goy,

00:11:28.427 --> 00:11:31.160
⟨de-⟩, nisht dem goy, nor ot dos gantse vinkl goyim,

00:11:31.160 --> 00:11:33.248
un zey zenen beyde arayngefaln.

00:11:33.338 --> 00:11:35.475
dos iz ⟨shoyn⟩ geven in dray un fertsikstn?

00:11:35.059 --> 00:11:37.280
dos iz geven in dray un fertsikstn yor.

00:11:37.725 --> 00:11:41.887
atsind ⟨vil ikh aykh⟩ dertseyln fun mayn bruder, vi azoy iz er gekumen tsu dem SHTUNDIST.

00:11:43.345 --> 00:11:46.697
s'i-, nor kh'vel shoyn frier derendikn fun zikh.

00:11:45.775 --> 00:11:46.748
bite.

00:11:48.171 --> 00:11:53.694
nu, ikh hob ongehoybn veynen. ikh hob gefilt, kh'hob gefilt instinktiv, kh'hob gefilt az mayne brider zenen dort arayn.

00:11:53.694 --> 00:11:57.905
mayn bruder ⟨shrekt⟩ un ikh hob nor gevolt aropgeyn, me zol mir hargenen. ikh hob nisht gevolt lebn mer.

00:11:57.905 --> 00:11:59.320
kh'hob mer nisht gevolt lebn.

00:12:00.405 --> 00:12:05.734
der bruder v- heybt on veynen, "vi vestu mir iberlozn mit tsvey kleyne kinder?" ⟨ot⟩ di kinder zenen shoyn geven ⟨shkeletn⟩.

00:12:05.734 --> 00:12:07.422
m'hot ge- m'hot gehungert.

00:12:07.422 --> 00:12:11.050
di, di, di, ikh fleg zitsn a gantse nakht un ikh hob zey gehitn,

00:12:11.050 --> 00:12:13.826
derfar vos di shtshures zenen arumgekrokhn oyf di kep

00:12:13.826 --> 00:12:15.150
un zey hobn moyre gehat.

00:12:15.150 --> 00:12:19.029
un d-dos yingele mit ⟨di⟩ meydele, zey hobn bakumen azoy vi... ikh bin geven reyn,

00:12:19.474 --> 00:12:23.360
mit di ⟨zelbe hor⟩ bin ikh geven, ikh bin geven reyn, un zey hobn bakum azoy fil layz,

00:12:23.360 --> 00:12:25.256
az ikh hob zikh nisht gekent keyn eytse gebn.

00:12:25.296 --> 00:12:27.770
keyn k⟨UNK⟩ iz nisht geven zikh vu tsu vashn.

00:12:28.823 --> 00:12:34.217
s'i-, s'iz, s'iz nisht tsum dertseyln. nisht tsum redn, nisht tsum dertseyln. ⟨di⟩ hunger un kelt!

00:12:37.615 --> 00:12:43.239
un s'iz gekumen a por tog, s'iz gekumen azoy NOVYY GOD, kumt arayn der goy un brengt arayn esn. zog ikh, "ANISKI,

00:12:43.239 --> 00:12:44.595
zog mir dem emes.

00:12:45.006 --> 00:12:48.054
vu zenen mayne tsvey brider? zenen nisht geven dortn?"

00:12:48.229 --> 00:12:50.540
nemt er, lozt arop azoy dem kop

00:12:50.997 --> 00:12:55.430
un entfert mir shoyn gornisht. hob ikh shoyn gevust az di brider zenen dort gefaln.

00:12:57.358 --> 00:13:02.853
⟨shoyn⟩, s'iz nishto shoyn mayne, ⟨di⟩, dos iz geven, UNK shoyn nishto di tsvey brider oykhet.

00:13:02.893 --> 00:13:05.371
dos iz shoyn geven in dray un fertsikstn yor,

00:13:05.371 --> 00:13:06.535
nokh a yor

00:13:06.535 --> 00:13:11.173
vi der bruder iz avek, fun, ikh vel bald dertseyln funem bruder, vi azoy er iz avek fun shtub.

00:13:11.702 --> 00:13:18.547
un, un, zitsn mir un mir vartn, ⟨un⟩ dray un fertsikstn yor iz geven zeyer a shlekht yor. s'hot zikh opgeshtelt der front barn ⟨STALININGRAD⟩.

00:13:18.992 --> 00:13:20.234
un dernokh

00:13:20.275 --> 00:13:22.800
hot men gevart, ot-ot-ot, ot-ot-ot,

00:13:23.228 --> 00:13:29.806
un di milkhome iz gegan, un undz ze'mir do geven, m'iz geven ni- nisht tsum lebn un nisht tsum toyt.

00:13:29.806 --> 00:13:32.097
m'iz gezitsn, di goye hot nisht gevolt haltn.

00:13:33.454 --> 00:13:37.093
der, der, der goy iz gevorn farkhapt oyf arbet.

00:13:37.690 --> 00:13:43.354
iz zi arayngekumen, hot zi gezogt, "⟨YA NE BACHILA KOLI VY UNK PRISHLI, YA NE KHOCHU BACHITI KOLI VY UNK PIDETE⟩."

00:13:43.596 --> 00:13:47.758
⟨un⟩ UNK ⟨zoln mir, zoln mir zikh⟩ shoyn farnemen, anisht geyt zi oyf ⟨di⟩ zhandarmerye meldn.

00:13:48.743 --> 00:13:50.391
azoy zenen mir gezitsn

00:13:50.447 --> 00:13:54.794
biz, der, der goy... draytsn teg gefast, on a trunk vaser.

00:13:55.257 --> 00:14:00.071
far di kinder oysgenart a broytele, gezogt az me geyt avek, hot zi arayngebrengt a broytele.

00:14:00.071 --> 00:14:02.547
m'hot es tseteylt, im halb un ir halb,

00:14:02.547 --> 00:14:05.966
un der bruder hot ⟨er nokh getun oykhet a bis; er hot nisht gekent⟩ oyshaltn dem hunger.

00:14:06.057 --> 00:14:08.332
ikh hob gefast. ikh ho-, biz haynt

00:14:08.332 --> 00:14:11.715
iz bay mir a tog, a fa- a, a tones iz gornisht.

00:14:11.862 --> 00:14:13.543
oyfn draytsetn tog

00:14:13.684 --> 00:14:18.029
bay nakht, emetser klapt. zayn simen iz geven, ot azoy hot er ongeklapt in der,

00:14:18.029 --> 00:14:19.044
in der strikhe.

00:14:19.945 --> 00:14:23.077
zog ikh, vek ikh oyf dem bruder, zog ikh, "ANISKI iz do."

00:14:23.657 --> 00:14:26.182
er kumt tsu, un zogt azoy:

00:14:27.808 --> 00:14:31.452
"me brent umedum. vu zey tretn, opbrenen zey."

00:14:32.230 --> 00:14:37.303
dos iz shoyn geven, dos iz shoyn geven, ⟨ven d- v-⟩, s'hot zikh untergerukt der front keyn Kovle.

00:14:37.596 --> 00:14:41.538
der front in Kovle iz geshtanen dray khadoshim tsayt, bay Kovle,

00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:44.154
un dos iz geven di ergste tsayt.

00:14:44.245 --> 00:14:46.401
dos iz shoyn geven dem fir un fertsikstn?

00:14:45.561 --> 00:14:48.592
dem fir un fertsikstn, yo. dos iz ⟨shoyn⟩ geven di ergste tsayt

00:14:48.632 --> 00:14:52.119
vos hot gekent zayn. zey hobn aroysgeyogt di goyim fun klinye,

00:14:52.547 --> 00:14:57.316
un, fun ⟨di shtiber⟩, un zey hobn gevoynt in shtub, un di goyim zenen geven in klinye.

00:14:58.318 --> 00:15:04.393
a- m'hot gehert az zey hobn gereykhert a tsigar, hob ikh gehert. ⟨az zey zenen arayngegan⟩ in BET SHIMUSH un zey hobn gereykhert a, a tsigar hob ikh gehert.

00:15:04.630 --> 00:15:09.259
un di goye iz arayngekumen, az me zol avek, me zol zikh aroysvarfn; di tvues zenen geven.

00:15:09.259 --> 00:15:13.731
⟨ah⟩, vi azoy zoln mir nor aroysgeyn? me ken ⟨zikh⟩ nisht aroysgeyn. me zol oyfraysn di, di strikhe

00:15:13.731 --> 00:15:15.831
un me zol zikh araynvarfn in di kanoplyes,

00:15:15.831 --> 00:15:17.364
un azoy zol men avekgeyn.

00:15:19.041 --> 00:15:24.245
⟨iz⟩ nishto vos tsu tun. s'iz nishto mit vemen tsu redn. der bruder zogt, "vos ⟨hos⟩tu f⟨UNK⟩ mit der goye?"

00:15:24.289 --> 00:15:27.365
zi vil nisht, zi, zi vil nisht farbrent vern, zogt zi, tsulib im,

00:15:27.365 --> 00:15:28.412
tsulib undz.

00:15:28.412 --> 00:15:30.791
zi hot a altn tatn, zogt zi, fun nayntsik yor.

00:15:30.791 --> 00:15:33.846
"far vos," zogt zi, "zol der tate farbrent vern tsulib aykh?"

00:15:34.178 --> 00:15:35.842
vos ir gekent entfern?

00:15:35.967 --> 00:15:37.682
gornisht gekent entfern!

00:15:38.312 --> 00:15:40.128
undz iz biter un fintster.

00:15:40.303 --> 00:15:44.904
vi, vi hot men gekent aropgeyn? dos meydele iz geven a geshvolene shtik fleysh, zi hot nisht gekent zikh rirn.

00:15:45.349 --> 00:15:47.604
dos yingele iz geven a lebediker mes.

00:15:47.138 --> 00:15:49.072
vi alt zenen zey geven, di kinder?

00:15:49.045 --> 00:15:52.869
dos meydele iz alt geven nayn yor, un dos yingele iz ⟨nisht⟩ geven alt akht yor.

00:15:56.284 --> 00:15:58.303
⟨nu, un⟩ der goy iz shoyn aheymgekumen,

00:15:58.360 --> 00:16:03.157
bet ikh oys, zog ikh, "dos yingele, dos yingele geyt oys." brengt arayn a,

00:16:03.157 --> 00:16:08.906
a shisele KONTSENTRAT, vos di daytshn hobn gevoynt dort, hobn zey ⟨oyfge-⟩ tep mit esn iz geven dort.

00:16:09.497 --> 00:16:12.179
un er est oyf dos shisele KONTSENTRAT

00:16:12.179 --> 00:16:14.334
un, un, un shtarbt shier avek,

00:16:14.779 --> 00:16:18.128
vos er hot nisht gegesn di gantse tsayt. dos iz geven fet.

00:16:18.795 --> 00:16:24.678
bet ikh oys a fleshele vaser mit a heyptele knobl mit a bisele zalts. mit dem hob ikh im geratevet ale mol.

00:16:26.912 --> 00:16:30.537
⟨un⟩ s'iz nisht geven, s'iz nisht geven vos tsu tun. s'iz nisht geven tsu vemen tsu redn.

00:16:30.537 --> 00:16:32.503
di shtshures zenen geven di khaveyrim,

00:16:32.503 --> 00:16:34.533
un di layz zenen arumgekrokhn,

00:16:34.962 --> 00:16:39.326
un keyn esn iz nishto, un m'iz hoyl naket. naket! in gantsn naket,

00:16:39.366 --> 00:16:40.963
vayl m'iz avek in eyn hemd.

00:16:42.876 --> 00:16:46.957
un der vinter, der vinter iz geven aza vinter in, dray un fertsikstn yor,

00:16:46.957 --> 00:16:50.094
az s'hot opgerisn di strikhe. azoyne vintn zenen geven.

00:16:50.094 --> 00:16:51.396
s'iz geven in APREL',

00:16:51.396 --> 00:16:55.233
ven der goy iz avek in kloyster arayn. er iz gekumen tsurik, hot er gezen az di strikhe iz opgerisn,

00:16:55.233 --> 00:16:57.146
un undz lign mir untern goln himl.

00:16:57.642 --> 00:17:00.471
er iz aroyfgekumen zuntik un er hot ⟨farlatet⟩ di strikhe.

00:17:02.822 --> 00:17:07.676
un azoy zenen mir gezitsn di gantse tsayt, in hunger un in kelt un in brud.

00:17:08.087 --> 00:17:12.184
un vos m'iz oysgeshtanen in der tsayt iz nisht tsum dertseyln, vayl ale mol,

00:17:12.184 --> 00:17:16.231
der, der goy hot gefirt a groysn kamf mit der goye az ⟨mir zoln⟩ zitsn.

00:17:16.440 --> 00:17:19.083
un dernokh iz der, der sheygets, der KHARTON,

00:17:19.123 --> 00:17:23.204
iz oykh avek in di partizaner. azoy fleg er aroysganvenen a por,

00:17:23.204 --> 00:17:25.800
a por PIROZHKIs un er fleg undz araynbrengen.

00:17:25.924 --> 00:17:29.664
un dernokh iz er avek in di partizaner un mir hobn nisht gehat ver s'zol undz epes derlangen.

00:17:30.075 --> 00:17:34.510
iz fun der gantser mishpokhe vos hot aykh oysgebahaltn, hot gevust der goy...?

00:17:34.294 --> 00:17:35.520
un di goye.

00:17:34.510 --> 00:17:37.546
der, der SHTUNDIST, zayn vayb, un der ⟨pli-⟩

00:17:36.167 --> 00:17:38.574
neyn! der goy iz nisht geven keyn SHTUNDIST.

00:17:38.243 --> 00:17:39.318
ah, neyn?

00:17:38.817 --> 00:17:39.891
neyn.

00:17:39.318 --> 00:17:40.768
der goy, zayn vayb....

00:17:40.555 --> 00:17:42.072
un vayter keyner nisht.

00:17:41.044 --> 00:17:42.744
u- un der pl⟨imenik⟩?

00:17:42.072 --> 00:17:43.839
der plimenik. yo, yo.

00:17:43.947 --> 00:17:46.809
vayter hot keyner nisht gevust. s'iz geven a alter foter,

00:17:46.933 --> 00:17:51.571
vos er hot nisht gezen. er fleg zikh arumdreyen. er hot a mol ongetapt, di hoyzn funem bruder.

00:17:51.571 --> 00:17:55.399
"OY," zogt er. "⟨N- NAPEVNO TUT KO MAYORKO BYL⟩." der tsveyter bruder.

00:17:55.438 --> 00:18:00.292
vayl m'iz geven, di, di brider, zey hobn gehandlt, zenen zey geven oysgekokht mit di goym.

00:17:57.177 --> 00:17:57.998
⟨KEN⟩!

00:18:01.446 --> 00:18:05.431
un azoy zenen mir gezitsn di gantse tsayt, ⟨un, un, un,⟩

00:18:05.431 --> 00:18:09.947
dos yingele iz geven oysgedart, dos meydele iz nor gezitsn mit di, gelegn mit farmakhte oygn,

00:18:09.947 --> 00:18:11.028
shoyn nisht keyn mentsh.

00:18:11.028 --> 00:18:13.679
dos yingele vos, ven er iz gezitsn gantse teg un nekht,

00:18:13.679 --> 00:18:17.707
kh'hob im oysgelernt, ⟨rekhenen⟩, ⟨MATEMATIKI⟩, ⟨TABLICHKI MNOZHENNYA⟩.

00:18:17.707 --> 00:18:19.847
kh'hob im oysgelernt di, di, di shtet.

00:18:19.847 --> 00:18:21.549
damlst hot nokh der kop gearbet,

00:18:21.549 --> 00:18:23.309
un ikh hob zeyer a sakh geleyent.

00:18:23.383 --> 00:18:28.625
 ikh hob im oysgelernt di, di, ale shtet fun der, fun der gantser velt, di, di, di ⟨STOLITSY⟩s.

00:18:28.952 --> 00:18:33.834
kh'hob im oysgelernt, ⟨, di, he,⟩ fun di politik. az er iz aheymgekumen hobn di, di,

00:18:33.834 --> 00:18:37.758
di komandirn gefregt, "fun vanet kenstu azoy politik?" er hot zikh, ⟨,⟩ farinteresirt mit dem.

00:18:37.758 --> 00:18:40.556
mit dem hob ikh im gekormet. dos iz geven zayn esn.

00:18:41.001 --> 00:18:42.530
dos iz geven zayn esn.

00:18:44.224 --> 00:18:46.006
un azoy zenen mir gezitsn

00:18:46.114 --> 00:18:48.690
bizn, fir un fertsikstn yor.

00:18:48.460 --> 00:18:49.586
yuli?

00:18:49.287 --> 00:18:51.981
yuli, bizn finef un tsvontsikstn yuli.

00:18:52.155 --> 00:18:58.050
 biz vanet, der, ⟨ot⟩ der goy iz antlofn fun der, fun, dortn. iz er avek in vald arayn,

00:18:58.050 --> 00:19:00.488
un er hot gezogt, undz zoln mir oykhet avekgeyn.

00:19:00.488 --> 00:19:03.422
un ⟨in⟩ dorf iz geven a toyt shtilkeyt,

00:19:03.529 --> 00:19:06.341
vayl di polya- di daytshn hobn opgetretn.

00:19:06.600 --> 00:19:08.804
yo, s'iz nokh geven nokh a sheyner fal.

00:19:08.828 --> 00:19:11.404
ven di daytshn hobn gevoynt, ⟨, bay⟩ di goyim,

00:19:11.494 --> 00:19:16.702
hobn zey gemakht... iz geven a fraytik, hobn zey tsenumen ale shtelekhlekh un zenen gegan makhn a MASARNIA,

00:19:16.860 --> 00:19:18.744
oyfn ⟨e-⟩ oyf vursht tsu makhn.

00:19:19.898 --> 00:19:27.064
un vos tut men? hot zey da- iz gekumen shoyn tsu bald tsu undzer shtelekhl. zey tsebrekhn ale mol dort di, ⟨a, a⟩ ander shtelekhl; m'hert ⟨nor⟩ di gevaldes.

00:19:27.103 --> 00:19:31.569
un ot-ot-ot kumen zey tsu tsu undzer shtelekhl un zi kumt arayn un veynt, di goye:

00:19:31.812 --> 00:19:35.417
me zol zikh aroysvarfn nokhn dakh, men zol zikh aroysvarfn nokhn dakh.

00:19:35.592 --> 00:19:40.041
vi hot men zikh gekent varfn az di, az dos meydele iz geven a kalike? m'iz aleyn geven kalikes.

00:19:40.232 --> 00:19:42.025
vos vet shoyn zayn vet zayn.

00:19:42.025 --> 00:19:45.072
hot got geholfn: a nes. m'hot UNK bloyz gelebt oyf nisim.

00:19:45.072 --> 00:19:48.114
⟨ah⟩, fraytik ⟨far, ⟩, azoy tsvishn tog un nakht,

00:19:48.265 --> 00:19:50.683
hert men vi, vi zey heybn on antloyfn.

00:19:50.683 --> 00:19:52.084
s'vert a,

00:19:52.084 --> 00:19:53.341
a rash,

00:19:53.341 --> 00:19:58.299
un zey heybn on antloyfn, vayl zey hobn derzen partizaner... zey flegn zeyer moyre hobn far di partizaner...

00:19:58.474 --> 00:20:00.049
un zenen antlofn.

00:20:00.049 --> 00:20:02.906
un oyf morgn, shabes, zenen arayngekumen andere daytshn.

00:20:03.132 --> 00:20:07.783
nu, andere daytshn zenen arayngekumen, un biz vanet zey hobn zikh shoyn ⟨ayngeordnt⟩, dervayl ze'mir undz gezitsn.

00:20:08.447 --> 00:20:14.426
vos me, m'iz, ⟨m'iz,⟩ oysgeshtanen in di dray khadoshim ve- ven zey, ven der front iz geshtanen bay Kovle, dos iz nisht tsum dertseyln.

00:20:14.426 --> 00:20:16.763
nisht tsum dertseyln ⟨vi azoy s'iz⟩ geven,

00:20:16.763 --> 00:20:20.864
⟨a, a⟩ gehenem iz geven! a gehenem. az di daytshn zenen arayngegan in shtub arayn

00:20:20.864 --> 00:20:24.945
un zey hobn gezogt, epes a kind veynt dortn. zey hobn gehert vi dos meydele hot ongehoybn veynen.

00:20:25.255 --> 00:20:26.853
epes a kind veynt dortn.

00:20:26.976 --> 00:20:29.265
hot di goye gezogt, "UNK epes a,

00:20:29.288 --> 00:20:32.225
a kind on eltern dreyt zikh do arum un zi veynt."

00:20:32.225 --> 00:20:34.125
di goye iz oysgeshtanen zeyer a sakh.

00:20:34.755 --> 00:20:36.491
nu, vi azoy geven der, der,

00:20:36.491 --> 00:20:38.245
der goy iz dokh nishto UNK.

00:20:38.245 --> 00:20:40.543
der goy fleg aroyfkumen ale zuntik.

00:20:40.543 --> 00:20:43.693
m'hot zikh gedorfn, ⟨m'iz azoy⟩, vi m'hot nisht geesn, ober ⟨aroysgang iz geven⟩.

00:20:44.188 --> 00:20:50.493
iz er, er hot avekgeshtelt a kestele, un ale zuntik iz er gekumen, er hot tsugenumen dos kestele, un ⟨er hot dos⟩ UNK bagrobn.

00:20:50.533 --> 00:20:52.513
