oyfn dritn tog, ⟨gegan⟩ der goy, ⟨hot zey⟩ geheysn aroysgeyn fun SKHRON

00:22:18.553 --> 00:22:20.212
un arayngeyn dort in a grub,

00:22:20.212 --> 00:22:24.909
un gebrengt tsvey politsyantn, ukraynishe, fun, fun, Holevne.

00:22:25.050 --> 00:22:29.932
un di tsvey politsyantn, er hot zey aray-, genumen di, mi- mit di biksn

00:22:29.932 --> 00:22:31.324
un m'hot zey geshosn.

