mayn bruder hot gegat a revolver,

00:22:34.146 --> 00:22:36.339
hot er zikh ongehoybn shteln mit zey,

00:22:36.339 --> 00:22:41.449
un er iz aroys naketerheyt. naketerheyt! zey hobn im ⟨op⟩geshosn finef mol, hot ⟨dertsey- nu,⟩ dertseylt a goy.

00:22:41.449 --> 00:22:43.657
finef mol, nor zey hobn im nisht getrofn.

00:22:44.271 --> 00:22:49.327
un azoy iz er antlofn tsun a tsveytn goy. er iz antlofn tsun a tsveytn goy,

00:22:49.536 --> 00:22:53.817
un er hot zikh opgevalgert, ⟨hot⟩ opgezukht dem tsveytn, dem klenern bruder,

00:22:53.817 --> 00:22:55.768
un ⟨zey⟩ zenen shoyn geven beyde tsuzamen.

00:22:55.768 --> 00:22:58.474
zenen zey avek, ⟨⟩, in, keyn Polap.

00:22:58.615 --> 00:23:01.815
dort zenen zey gezitsn bay a goy, v⟨UNK⟩ der goy hot zey gehaltn.

00:23:01.838 --> 00:23:04.121
un, m'hot nokh gezukht alts yidn.

00:23:04.121 --> 00:23:07.687
iz men gekumen tsu dem goy vos m'hot gevust az er hot gehandlt mit im.

00:23:07.693 --> 00:23:10.567
m'hot aroysgevorfn dos gantse klinye mit shtroy!

00:23:10.567 --> 00:23:12.795
m'hot shoyn kimat ongetretn oyf zeyere fis,

00:23:12.795 --> 00:23:13.947
un m'iz avek.

00:23:14.781 --> 00:23:17.070
hobn zey shoyn gemuzt baytn dem plats.

00:23:17.937 --> 00:23:22.127
m'hot gebitn dem plats, un zey zenen avek UNK oykhet keyn Kosnishtsh.

00:23:22.127 --> 00:23:23.308
in Kosnishtsh

00:23:23.308 --> 00:23:27.197
hobn ⟨zey⟩ zikh arumgeblonket. vu zey hobn getogt hobn zey nisht genekhtikt.

00:23:27.370 --> 00:23:32.106
un zenen geven akht tog UNK dertseylt zenen zey geven oyfn shney untern goln himl.

00:23:32.331 --> 00:23:34.834
un di beste goyim, di beste pletser,

00:23:34.834 --> 00:23:38.923
m'hot nisht gevolt tsulozn. m'hot gevo-, m'hot nisht gevolt gebn keyn trunk, afile.

00:23:39.925 --> 00:23:42.973
dernokh, ⟨az zey zenen⟩ shoyn gegan un gebitn dem plats,

00:23:43.232 --> 00:23:47.810
