00:23:59.196 --> 00:24:03.715
ir zent bafrayt gevorn bay di sovyetn, hot ir gezogt, yuli fir un fertsik.

00:24:03.297 --> 00:24:04.928
fir un fertsik, yo.

00:24:04.427 --> 00:24:06.547
vos geshet demlst n⟨UNK⟩?

00:24:06.334 --> 00:24:07.965
m'iz bafrayt ge-

00:24:06.874 --> 00:24:08.685
bald nokhn bafrayen?

00:24:08.005 --> 00:24:13.410
b- bald nokhn bafrayen ⟨iz,⟩ geven azoy: s'iz arayn un me hot shoyn gehert, undz ze'mir gev- zitsn ⟨eyne⟩ in klinye.

00:24:13.410 --> 00:24:15.941
mit di shiserayen, di bombardirungen, di,

00:24:15.941 --> 00:24:19.215
un arum un arum iz farbrent gevorn di shtiber, afile di tserkev.

00:24:19.215 --> 00:24:22.629
un dos shtibl iz ⟨bay⟩, al-pi nes iz farblibn. alts iz geven mit nisim.

00:24:23.715 --> 00:24:26.329
un s'iz shoyn arayn, m'hert shoyn, "DAVAY SYUDA.

00:24:26.329 --> 00:24:31.753
DAVAY SYUDA." s'iz arayn shrapneln tsishn... ikh bin gezitsn mitn meydele un der bruder iz gezitsn in eyn vinkl mitn yingele.

00:24:31.753 --> 00:24:34.167
tsishn undz beyde arayn etlekhene shrapneln.

00:24:34.167 --> 00:24:35.700
nisht geshodt gornisht.

00:24:37.452 --> 00:24:39.167
m'iz bafrayt gevorn.

00:24:40.742 --> 00:24:43.267
undz ze'mir nokh nisht aropgegan funem boydem.

00:24:44.691 --> 00:24:50.619
m'hert shoyn "DAVAY SYUDA," iz shoyn a simen ⟨azoy⟩. d- bald der KHARTON iz gekumen tsu loyfn, zen tsi undz ze'mir nokh do.

00:24:50.619 --> 00:24:52.481
er iz gegan mit di partizaner.

00:24:53.871 --> 00:24:56.399
dos iz geven, ⟨d-⟩mitvokh, donershtik.

00:24:56.399 --> 00:25:00.024
der bruder zogt, er geyt avek in shtot arayn zen tsi s'iz emetser do.

00:25:00.925 --> 00:25:03.792
er hot undz ibergelozt, un er iz avekgegan in shtot arayn.

00:25:03.792 --> 00:25:05.700
hot im bald a shtab farkhapt.

00:25:05.937 --> 00:25:09.461
m'hot im gevolt, oysfregn, ver er iz, vos er iz,

00:25:09.461 --> 00:25:14.111
un er zol vayzn dem plats, vu m'iz geven farbahaltn. hot er nisht gevolt vayzn,

00:25:14.111 --> 00:25:16.613
vayl m'hot, der goy hot zikh gehitn far di goyim.

00:25:17.732 --> 00:25:24.003
iz er avekgegan in shtot arayn. m'hot im avekgefirt in shtot arayn, keyn Libevne, un m'hot im dortn gehaltn a tog tsayt,

00:25:24.921 --> 00:25:32.204
biz vanet er iz tsurikgekumen. iz, der goy ⟨hot⟩ gezogt, m'hot im shoyn geharget oyfn veg, vayl damlst ⟨iz nokh⟩ gegan di milkhome, un m'hot geharget.

00:25:32.515 --> 00:25:38.651
un, shtelt zikh for mayn lage. ikh hob UNK geblibn mit tsvey kalikes. vos zol ikh tun? mit tsvey kalikes geblibn!

00:25:39.298 --> 00:25:43.291
oyf zuntik iz er gekumen. shabes far nakht iz er gekumen tsu geyn,

00:25:43.872 --> 00:25:49.046
un m'iz aropgegan zuntik far tog, f- tsvey a zeyger, azoy vi s'hot ongehoybn vern likhtik,

00:25:49.103 --> 00:25:51.358
az keyner zol nit zen vi me geyt arop.

00:25:51.381 --> 00:25:54.817
zenen mir gegan fun tsvey bay nakht biz akht. m'hot nisht gekent geyn.

00:25:55.667 --> 00:25:57.802
m'iz aheymgegan in shtub arayn.

00:25:57.802 --> 00:25:59.541
zayn shtub iz nokh geshtanen.

00:26:00.308 --> 00:26:01.894
m'iz aheymgekumen.

00:26:01.894 --> 00:26:03.727
vey! shray!

00:26:03.885 --> 00:26:06.849
s'iz nishto tsu vemen tsu redn, s'iz nishto tsu vemen tsu shrayen.

00:26:07.446 --> 00:26:10.832
m'iz avekgegan, s'iz nokh geven f⟨UNK⟩ yidn un m'iz tsurikgekumen, keyner nishto.

00:26:11.631 --> 00:26:13.835
un m'iz aheymgekumen mit tsvey kalikes.

00:26:14.466 --> 00:26:16.437
un der bruder aleyn oykhet a kalike.

00:26:16.437 --> 00:26:20.012
ikh ⟨bin⟩ zikh shoyn, ikh hob zikh shoyn gehaltn beser fun zey ale.

00:26:34.581 --> 00:26:36.583
he, m'iz aheymgekumen,

00:26:38.310 --> 00:26:42.843
bald iz, ⟨,⟩ geven der, ⟨s'iz a⟩ ⟨POGONIĆ⟩ in shtot. s'zenen bald arayn a sakh ⟨VOYENNY⟩.

00:26:42.850 --> 00:26:44.821
m'hot gezen vi azoy m'iz farblibn,

00:26:44.821 --> 00:26:46.842
hot men ongehoybn araynbrengen esn.

00:26:48.165 --> 00:26:53.756
m'hot ongehoybn ⟨arge-⟩ araynbrengen esn di kinder, ⟨me, m'hot zey⟩, mit di kendelekh hobn zey gebrengt fun der kikh.

00:26:53.756 --> 00:26:55.432
hobn zey gebrengt esn,

00:26:55.843 --> 00:26:59.600
un, un, un di, di kinder zenen geven nisht enlekh tsu keyn mentshn.

00:26:59.758 --> 00:27:01.001
nisht keyn mentshn!

00:27:01.429 --> 00:27:05.370
biz vanet s'hot gedovert a sheyne por yor, biz vanet zey zenen aroys fun dem.

00:27:05.142 --> 00:27:07.380
hot ir geblibn etlekhe yor in Libevne?

00:27:07.251 --> 00:27:08.088
yo.

00:27:08.213 --> 00:27:12.088
s'iz, s'iz geven nokh epes yidn vos zey hobn zikh geratevet fun ayer gegnt?

00:27:10.440 --> 00:27:14.942
dernokh, yo. dernokh iz aroyfgekumen nokh etlekhene mishpokhes,

00:27:14.942 --> 00:27:16.731
vos zenen geven ⟨oykh⟩ oysfarbahaltn.

00:27:16.731 --> 00:27:19.310
m'iz shoyn geven a tsvontsik, draysik yidn.

00:27:19.587 --> 00:27:23.631
un dernokh, in fir un fertsikstn yor iz aropgekumen a komisye fun, Moskve:

00:27:23.890 --> 00:27:25.723
a dokter, a prokuror...

00:27:28.497 --> 00:27:32.271
 dray mentshn zenen zey aropgekumen, un m'iz gegan efenen di griber.

00:27:32.850 --> 00:27:35.274
m'hot geefnt di griber oyf der tsigelnye.

00:27:35.331 --> 00:27:38.154
dos iz nisht tsum redn un nisht tsum dertseyln.

00:27:38.436 --> 00:27:43.543
dem, di yidn zenen gelign ayngeprest, azoy vi me efnt oyf, ⟨oyb ir hot⟩ a mol gezen a fas hering.

00:27:43.650 --> 00:27:45.664
ayngeprest eyner inem andern.

00:27:45.664 --> 00:27:47.391
⟨un zey⟩ zenen nokh gelign gants.

00:27:47.616 --> 00:27:54.472
