00:28:19.898 --> 00:28:21.343
d-dem hunger,

00:28:21.585 --> 00:28:22.822
di shrek,

00:28:22.822 --> 00:28:25.038
dem pakhed, dem brud.

00:28:25.872 --> 00:28:31.656
