00:28:35.179 --> 00:28:37.034
tsvey ukrayner hobn zey gekhapt,

00:28:37.034 --> 00:28:39.694
un m'hot zey gefirt, tsu der, tsu der, ⟨p-⟩

00:28:39.694 --> 00:28:41.019
tsu dem komisar,

00:28:41.076 --> 00:28:44.514
tsu dem GEBIETSKOMMISSAR. dort zenen geven ale yidn farnumen.

00:28:44.514 --> 00:28:49.181
un zey hobn zikh aroysgeganvet un zey hobn gevust ⟨di veld-⟩ zenen geven, zey hobn gekent dos ⟨dorf gut⟩,

00:28:49.181 --> 00:28:50.536
un m'iz antlofn.

00:28:50.695 --> 00:28:54.553
dernokh zenen zey arayngefaln, zenen zey arayngefaln tsurik.

00:28:54.576 --> 00:28:57.526
⟨, oys, m'hot zey,⟩ vu m'hot zey gezukht,

00:28:57.526 --> 00:28:59.593
un vu m'hot zey ge- nisht gefunen...

00:28:59.593 --> 00:29:02.984
un dernokh, in dray un fertsikstn yor, ven m'hot shoyn nisht geklert fun keyn yidn...

00:29:02.984 --> 00:29:07.053
zey hobn zikh opgemutshet aza yor tsayt, un zenen arayngefaln beyde tsuzamen,

00:29:07.053 --> 00:29:08.790
in eyn, in eyn minut.
